The submodules are CommonJS, i.e. `module.exports = Channel;` and similar. The index.js is

```js
module.exports = {
    IncomingFrameStream:  require('./lib/IncomingFrameStream'),
    OutgoingFrameStream:  require('./lib/OutgoingFrameStream'),
    //...
};
```

How should I have written the type definition for that?

